
Overview of noun ladle

The noun ladle has 1 sense (no senses from tagged texts)
                                         
1. ladle -- (a spoon-shaped vessel with a long handle; frequently used to transfer liquids from one container to another)

Overview of verb ladle

The verb ladle has 2 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. ladle -- (put (a liquid) into a container by means of a ladle; "ladle soup into the bowl")
2. ladle, lade, laden -- (remove with or as if with a ladle; "ladle the water out of the bowl")
